OL,3,CCharles pays tribute to 'darling Mama'
OL,4,Cin heartfelt video message
OL,6,FThe King has recorded a heartfelt
OL,7,Ftribute to his "darling Mama" to mark
OL,8,Fthe centenary of her birth but said
OL,9,Fmuch of much of life today would
OL,10,Flikely have "troubled her deeply".
OL,12,FCharles' video message in tribute to
OL,13,Fthe nation's longest-reigning monarch
OL,14,Fdescribes how "she remained constant,
OL,15,Fsteadfast and wholly devoted to the
OL,16,Fpeople she served".
OL,26,@oD@POUoD@]O]rD@MOUrD@aO]vD@OOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
