FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776735419
OL,3,CCharles pays tribute to 'darling Mama'
OL,4,Cin heartfelt video message
OL,6,FHe acknowledged the many challenges
OL,7,Fand issues nationally and across the
OL,8,Fglobe that may have caused her reason
OL,9,Ffor concern, and renewed his "own
OL,10,Fsolemn pledge of duty and service to
OL,11,Fyou all".
OL,13,FThe late Queen would have turned 100
OL,14,Fon April 21 and the King said her
OL,15,Fexistence should be celebrated as a
OL,16,F"life well-lived" rather than marking
OL,17,Fan "absence" ahead of a series of
OL,18,Froyal events that will honour her
OL,19,Fduring Tuesday.
OL,26,@qD@^OUsD@HO]xD@AOUxD@QO]yD@DOUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776735419
OL,3,CCharles pays tribute to 'darling Mama'
OL,4,Cin heartfelt video message
OL,6,F"Much about the times we now live in,
OL,7,FI suspect, may have troubled her
OL,8,Fdeeply, but I take heart from her
OL,9,Fbelief that goodness will always
OL,10,Fprevail and that a brighter dawn is
OL,11,Fnever far from the horizon," the King
OL,12,Fsaid in his message.
OL,14,FHe added: "For, as a young Princess
OL,15,FElizabeth put it in her first ever
OL,16,Fpublic broadcast, aged just 14, we can
OL,17,Feach play our part 'to make the world
OL,18,Fof tomorrow a better and happier
OL,19,Fplace'.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@\O]vD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
