PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776735419
OL,3,CCharles pays tribute to 'darling Mama'
OL,4,Cin heartfelt video message
OL,6,FFor the woman who was never meant to
OL,7,Fbe sovereign, the Queen fulfilled her
OL,8,Fpledge to serve nation and
OL,9,FCommonwealth, and came to earn the
OL,10,Frespect of many ` from world leaders
OL,11,Fto the public.
OL,13,FShe became one of the most iconic
OL,14,Ffaces of the 20th century who
OL,15,Fepitomised much that was identified as
OL,16,FBritish while at home her love of
OL,17,Fhorse and dogs defined the Queen as
OL,18,Fmuch as her role as head of state.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776735419
OL,3,CCharles pays tribute to 'darling Mama'
OL,4,Cin heartfelt video message
OL,6,FIn the video tribute, filmed in the
OL,7,Flibrary at Balmoral Castle in early
OL,8,FApril, the King adds: "Queen
OL,9,FElizabeth's 'promise with destiny
OL,10,Fkept' shaped the world around her and
OL,11,Ftouched the lives of countless people
OL,12,Facross our nation, the Commonwealth
OL,13,Fand beyond.
OL,15,F"Her near-century was one of
OL,16,Fremarkable change and yet, through
OL,17,Feach passing decade, through every
OL,18,Ftransformation, she remained constant,
OL,19,Fsteadfast and wholly devoted to the
OL,20,Fpeople she served.
OL,26,@pD@WOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776735419
OL,3,CCharles pays tribute to 'darling Mama'
OL,4,Cin heartfelt video message
OL,6,F"Millions will remember her for
OL,7,Fmoments of national significance; many
OL,8,Fothers for a fleeting personal
OL,9,Fencounter, a smile, a kind word that
OL,10,Flifted spirits ... or for that
OL,11,Fmarvellous twinkle of the eye when
OL,12,Fsharing a marmalade sandwich with
OL,13,FPaddington Bear in the final months of
OL,14,Fher life."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
