CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776735419
OL,3,CCharles pays tribute to 'darling Mama'
OL,4,Cin heartfelt video message
OL,6,FCharles concluded his message by
OL,7,Furging all to follow the late Queen's
OL,8,F"example" and improve the world around
OL,9,Fus: "So, young or old, and whatever
OL,10,Four differences, let us therefore seek
OL,11,Fto follow this example as we make
OL,12,Ftoday not the marking of a milestone
OL,13,Ffelt by absence but the celebration of
OL,14,Fa life well-lived, and a legacy of
OL,15,Fhope, as we strive together towards a
OL,16,F'better, happier tomorrow' ` one
OL,17,Frooted in peace, justice, prosperity
OL,18,Fand security."
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@IO]qD@EOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
