OL,3,CCharles pays tribute to 'darling Mama'
OL,4,Cin heartfelt video message
OL,6,FHe ended by addressing his mother:
OL,7,F"God bless you, darling Mama; you
OL,8,Fremain forever in our hearts and
OL,9,Fprayers."
OL,11,FDuring the day, members of the
OL,12,Fmonarchy will visit the British Museum
OL,13,Fto see a scale model of the Queen
OL,14,FElizabeth Memorial with architect Lord
OL,15,FFoster, who won the bid to design the
OL,16,Fnational monument, during a reception
OL,17,Fattended by the prime minister.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@IO]
